<%= render "image_front", sticky: true %>

<div class="container">
  <div class="frame-shape home-wrap">
    <br><h3><%= "LeagueBox website structure".upcase %></h3>
    <br><h5>Home</h5>
    <p>General presentation of the Box League Tournament</p>
    <p>Footpage links to <span class="colored-text">Tournament rules</span>, <span class="colored-text">Club staff</span>, <span class="colored-text">Website map</span>,
    <% if current_user && current_user.role == "admin" %><span class="colored-text">Create club</span>,<% end %> <span class="colored-text">Log in</span> (unless already logged in).</p>

    <br><h5>Tournament overview and rules</h5>
    <p>Explanation of the of the Box League rules</p>
    <p>Footpage links to <span class="colored-text">Home</span>, <span class="colored-text">Club staff</span>, and <span class="colored-text">Website map</span>.</p>

    <br><h5>Club staff</h5>
    <p>Details of the admin and the club referee</p>
    <p>Footpage links to <span class="colored-text">Home</span>, <span class="colored-text">Tournament rules</span>, <span class="colored-text">Website map</span>
    <% if current_user && current_user.role == "player" %>, and <span class="colored-text">Enter my results</span><% end %>.</p>

    <br><h5>All Boxes</h5>
    <p>Display all boxes in one glance with following details for each player:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>name</li>
      <li>ranking in the club</li>
      <li>number of matches played</li>
      <li>number of total points</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Current player appears in <span style= "color:green">green</span>.</p>
    <% if current_user && current_user.role != "player" %>
      <p>Clicking on a box leads to the Box Referee view.</p>
      <p>Footpage button links to <span class="colored-text">League table</span>.</p>
    <% else %>
      <p>Clicking on a box leads to the Box Table view.</p>
      <p>Footpage links to <span class="colored-text">League table</span>, and <span class="colored-text">Enter my results</span> (= Manage my box page).</p>
    <% end %>

    <br><h5>League table</h5>
    <p>Each player appears in descending rank order under the headers <strong>Player, Rank, Points, Box, Matches </strong>(matches played)<strong>,
    Won </strong>(matches won)<strong>, Sets </strong>(sets played)<strong>, Won </strong>(sets won).</p>
    <p>Clicking on a header sorts the player according to this header.</p>
    <p>Footpage links to <span class="colored-text">Back to top</span>, and <span class="colored-text">All boxes</span>.</p>

    <% if current_user && current_user.role != "player" %>
      <br><h5>Box referee view</h5>
      <p>Each player's matches which have been played are shown as list items. Headers are <strong>Match scores,
      Player match points, Opponent match points, Opponent's total points</strong>.
      Unplayed matchs are listed too.</p>
      <p>Clicking on a match line lands on the Match Edit/Delete page, clicking on an unplayed match (admin only) lands on the New match score page.</p>

    <% else %>
      <br><h5>Box Table view</h5>
      <p>Each player's matches are shown under their corresponding opponent.</p>
      <p>Current player appears in <span style= "color:green">green</span>.</p>
      <p>Toggle link to <span class="colored-text">List view</span>.</p>

      <br><h5>Box List view</h5>
      <p>Each player's matches which have been played are shown as list items. Headers are <strong>Match scores,
      Player match points, Opponent match points, Opponent's total points</strong>.</p>
      <p>Current player appears in <span style= "color:green">green</span>, and a <span class="colored-text">Enter new results</span> link to Manage my box is shown.</p>
      <p>Toggle link to <span class="colored-text">Table view</span>.</p>

      <br><h5>Manage my box</h5>
      <p>Each of my box matches dates and players points with links such as <span class="colored-text">Display my box</span>, <span class="colored-text">See match results</span>, and <span class="colored-text">Enter new score</span>.</p>
    <% end %>

    <br><h5>Match results view</h5>
    <p>Details of a match played:
    <ul>
      <li>game date and time, court number,</li>
      <li>score, with date and time of submission,</li>
      <li>match earnings and total points.</li>
    </ul></p>

    <br><h5>New match score</h5>
    <p>Form to enter new match details.</p>

    <% if current_user && current_user.role != "player" %>
      <br><h5>Match edit score</h5>
      <p>Form to modify match details, or delete score.</p>
    <% end %>

  </div><br>

  <div class = "buttons-wrap">
    <%= link_to "Tournament rules", rules_path, class: "btn buttons-shape btn-green" %>
    <%= link_to "Club staff", staff_path, class: "btn buttons-shape btn-green" %>
    <% if current_user && current_user.role == "admin" %>
      <%= link_to "New round", new_user_box_score_path, class: "btn buttons-shape btn-green" %>
    <% end %>
    <% unless current_user %>
      <%= link_to "Log in to enter new match results", new_user_session_path, class: "btn buttons-shape btn-green" %>
    <% end %>
    <%= link_to "Back to top", "#", class: "btn buttons-shape btn-blue" %>
  </div>
</div>
